Count Tokens
import java.util.StringTokenizer;

public class Demo {

    public static void main(String[] args) {

        StringTokenizer st =
                new StringTokenizer("Java Spring SQL");

        System.out.println(st.countTokens());
    }
}
Output
3

Important Methods
Method	Description
hasMoreTokens()	Returns true if more tokens are available
nextToken()	Returns the next token
countTokens()	Returns the number of remaining tokens
nextToken(String delimiter)	Changes the delimiter and returns the next token

